Revision history for WWW-Shodan-API

0.021 2026-03-27
    - Refactored internal _request method to support GET, POST, PUT, and DELETE
      with JSON and form-encoded request bodies
    - Added search_facets, search_filters
    - Added on-demand scanning: ports, protocols, scan, scan_internet, scans, scan_status
    - Added network alerts: create_alert, alerts_info, alert_info, edit_alert,
      delete_alert, alert_triggers, enable_trigger, disable_trigger,
      add_whitelist, remove_whitelist, add_notifier, remove_notifier
    - Added notifiers: notifiers, notifier_providers, notifier_info,
      create_notifier, edit_notifier, delete_notifier
    - Added directory methods: queries, search_queries, query_tags
    - Added account method: profile
    - Added DNS method: domain_info
    - Added utility method: http_headers
    - Simplified query and facet string building (extracted _build_query_str
      and _build_facets_str helpers)

0.010 2014-xx-xx
    - Bubble up API errors in HTTP response body

0.009 2014-xx-xx
    - Initial CPAN release
